    "Following this step, three coders were trained to annotate text sections with the corresponding learning tips (see Table 3 for the exact codes).",
    "The internal recommender feature of INCEpTION was activated.",
    "First, in a pilot phase, all three coders coded the same 100 essays.",
    "Following this, the average agreement between all coders was measured.",
    "For this purpose, we calculated the individual agreement between all pairs of coders with the help of Cohen's Kappa (McHugh, 2012)."
